data.description: Welcome to your new home in the desirable Soaring Eagles neighborhood! This meticulously maintained 2-story residence with a finished basement is move-in ready and offers breathtaking mountain views. Enjoy the convenience of being close to schools, parks, Fort Carson, Peterson AFB, and the bustling Powers Corridor, with its abundance of shopping and dining options. The main level boasts an open and bright floor plan, featuring a cozy fireplace in the living room that seamlessly flows into the dining area and kitchen. Step outside onto the spacious brick patio in the fenced backyard, perfect for outdoor gatherings. Experience the ease of main level living with a master bedroom and attached bath just down the hall. Upstairs, you’ll find two bedrooms and another full bath, providing ample space for your family. The finished basement offers a large family room, an additional bedroom, and another full bath, ensuring everyone has their own space. This gem won’t be on the market for long, so don’t miss out—schedule your private showing today! PS: don't forget to check out video tour.
